trans-unit.source: Retrieves exports provided by a collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Recupera as exportações fornecidas por uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: This type implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Este tipo implementa o <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.

trans-unit.source: When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.
trans-unit.target: Quando você terminar de usar o tipo, descarte-direta ou indiretamente.

trans-unit.source: To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a `try`/`catch` block.
trans-unit.target: Para descartar o tipo diretamente, chame seu <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> método em um `try` / `catch` bloco.

trans-unit.source: To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para descartar indiretamente dele, use uma construção de linguagem, como `using` (em c#) ou `Using` (no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Using an Object that Implements IDisposable" section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte a seção "Usando um objeto que implementa IDisposable" o <xref:System.IDisposable> tópico de interface.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: The prioritized list of export providers.
trans-unit.target: A lista priorizada de provedores de exportação.

trans-unit.source: The providers are consulted in the order in which they are supplied.
trans-unit.target: Os provedores são consultados na ordem em que são fornecidos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> class consults the providers in the order in which they have been specified when it calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider.GetExports%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> classe consulta os provedores na ordem em que eles foram especificados quando chama <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider.GetExports%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> does not take ownership of the specified providers.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> não apropriar-se dos provedores especificados.

trans-unit.source: That is, it tries to dispose of any of the providers when it is disposed.
trans-unit.target: Ou seja, ele tenta descartar qualquer um dos provedores de quando ele é descartado.

trans-unit.source: One or more elements of <paramref name="providers" /> are <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Um ou mais elementos de <paramref name="providers" /> são <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The prioritized list of export providers.
trans-unit.target: A lista priorizada de provedores de exportação.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> class consults the providers in the order in which they have been specified when it calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider.GetExports%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> classe consulta os provedores na ordem em que eles foram especificados quando chama <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider.GetExports%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> does not take ownership of the specified providers.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> não apropriar-se dos provedores especificados.

trans-unit.source: That is, it tries to dispose of any of the providers when it is disposed.
trans-unit.target: Ou seja, ele tenta descartar qualquer um dos provedores de quando ele é descartado.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos usados pela classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pela instância atual da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar `Dispose` quando tiver terminado de usar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose` método deixa o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> em um estado inutilizável.

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar `Dispose`, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> para o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> estava ocupando.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Sempre chamar `Dispose` antes de liberar sua última referência para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider>.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider> do objeto `Finalize` método.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> para liberar recursos gerenciados e não gerenciados; <see langword="false" /> para liberar apenas recursos não gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> class and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pela classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> e, opcionalmente, libera os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: The conditions of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export" /> objects to be returned.
trans-unit.target: As condições dos objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export" /> a serem retornados.

trans-unit.source: The transactional container for the composition.
trans-unit.target: O contêiner transacional para a composição.

trans-unit.source: Gets all the exports that match the conditions of the specified import.
trans-unit.target: Obtém todas as exportações que correspondem às condições da importação especificada.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains all the exports that match the specified condition.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção que contém todas as exportações que correspondem à condição especificada.

trans-unit.source: Implementers should not treat cardinality-related mismatches as errors and are not expected to throw exceptions in those cases.
trans-unit.target: Os implementadores não devem tratar incompatibilidades de cardinalidade como erros e não deverão gerar exceções nesses casos.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the import requests exactly one export and the provider has either no matching exports or more than one, the method should return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se a importação solicita exatamente uma exportação e o provedor tem nenhum exportações de correspondência ou em mais de um, o método deve retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> coleção de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.Export>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that contains the providers that the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> object aggregates.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção que contém os provedores que o objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> agrega.

trans-unit.source: A collection of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider" /> objects that the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> aggregates.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção do <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ExportProvider" /> objetos que o <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> agregações.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> object has been disposed of.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.AggregateExportProvider" /> foi descartado.
